Cardinal Edward Egan insisted Saturday that he properly handled allegations of sexual abuse by priests.
<P>


<font  face="times new roman"><b><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2002/03/24/nyregion/24COMP.html?todaysheadlines">Crime-Fighting by Computer Widens Scope</a></b><br>
